---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 433
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=The False Light
By: Walter Hilton
---
Light of knowing that is feigned by the fiend to a murk soul is aye
showed atwixt two black rainy clouds. The over cloud is presumption
and highing of himself; the nether cloud is down putting and lowing of
his even-christian.
